{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "第十九回\"管鲍之交\"讲述阿吉与铁虎（真名雷震天）的决战。铁虎以一串鞭神功发动攻势，阿吉却以一段枯枝为剑，借力打力，用铁虎自身的力量击碎其全身骨节。铁虎临死前追问剑法来历，阿吉答以\"专破一串鞭的剑法\"。战后阿吉与哑巴夫妇告别，哑巴之妻尖锐指责阿吉利用他们，但阿吉与哑巴以握手传达无言的信任。场景转至大老板府邸，竹叶青向大老板汇报铁虎死讯，大老板震怒之下追问细节，竹叶青透露已安排高手对付阿吉。铁手阿勇在铁虎尸体前恸哭，质问竹叶青铁虎之死的真正原因。夜色中竹叶青通过驼背老人进入秘密地窖，发现哑巴夫妇被绑架至此。竹叶青以金银引诱哑巴之妻说出交手细节，哑巴之妻为黄金出卖秘密，哑巴愤怒之下掐死妻子，随后撞墙自尽。竹叶青冷眼旁观这一切，事后与紫铃幽会，感叹大老板终究比他更强。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "雷震天",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "我知道你自己也曾说过，要做天下无敌的剑客，就一定要无情，现在呢？现在你已经变了，你已不再是那天下无敌的剑客，这一战你必败无疑。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "雷震天",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "其实你是否去杀他们，我根本不在乎，只要能杀了你，他们能往哪里走？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "雷震天",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你的人虽然变了，可是你的人仍在，你的剑呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "雷震天",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "这就是你的剑？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "text": "我的人变了，我的剑也变了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "雷震天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "雷震天",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "这是什么剑法？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "text": "这就是专破一串鞭的剑法。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "雷震天",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "好，好……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_ya_ba",
      "text": "虽然你不会说话，可是你心里想说的话我都知道。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_ya_ba",
      "text": "我相信你绝不会泄漏我的秘密，我绝对信任你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_ya_ba",
      "text": "他带给我们的只有麻烦，你为什么还要这样对他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "又是那个阿吉下的毒手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我想不到他这么快就找到阿吉，更想不到会死得这么惨。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "他还没有死之前，全身的骨节就已全都被打碎了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "是被什么东西打碎的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我看不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我只看出阿吉用的绝不是刀剑，也不是铁器。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你凭哪点看出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "铁虎衣服上并没有被铁器打过的痕迹，也没有被划破，只留着些木屑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "难道那个阿吉用的只不过是根木棍？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "很可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你知不知道铁虎练的是什么功夫？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "好像是金钟罩，铁布衫一类的外门功夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你有没有看过真功夫？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我看过，就因为他功夫实在太强，所以我连他的来历都没有十分清楚，就将他收容下来。后来我才知道，他就是昔年曾在辽北横行过一时的'云中金刚'崔老三。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我也听大老板说过。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "虽然他曾经被雷震天逼得无路可走，可是我保证他的功夫绝不比那个姓雷的差太多，也绝不会比祁连山那个玉霸王差到哪里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "可是现在你居然说那个没有用的阿吉只凭一根木棍就能将他的全身骨节打碎？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "他的尸身是在哪里找到的？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是在韩大奶奶那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "那里又不是坟场，总有几个人看见他们交手的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "他们交手的地方，是在厨房后面一个堆垃圾和木柴的小院子里。姑娘们都很少到那里去，所以当时在场的，除了阿吉和铁虎外，最多只有三个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "哪三个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "韩大奶奶，和一对烧饭的哑巴厨子夫妻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "现在你是不是已经把他们的人带了回来？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "因为他们已经被阿吉杀了灭口！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "好，好，我养了你们这么多人，养了你们这么多年，你们竟连一个挑粪的小子都对付不了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都为什么还不卷起铺盖来走路！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "因为我们还要等几个人。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "等谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "等几个可以去对付阿吉的人。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你有把握？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "先说一个人的名字给我听。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "他们什么时候可以到？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "最迟明天下午。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "好，替我安排，明天下午见阿吉。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我就知道无论什么事你都会替我安排好的。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "今天晚上，你可以好好的睡一觉了，明天也不妨迟些起来，那个女人……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "text": "我知道，我绝不会辜负大老板对我的好意！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_lao_ban",
      "speaker_name": "大老板",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "好，好极了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_tie_shou_a_yong",
      "text": "大丈夫有泪不轻弹，人死不能复生，你哭什么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shou_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁手阿勇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我哭的不是他，是我自己！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shou_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁手阿勇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "因为我总算看见了替大老板做事的人，会有什么样的下场！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_tie_shou_a_yong",
      "text": "大老板待人并不坏。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shou_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁手阿勇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "可是现在铁虎死了，大老板至少也应该安排安排他的后事才对……",
