      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_tie_shou_a_yong",
      "text": "大老板知道我会替他安排的！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_shou_a_yong",
      "speaker_name": "铁手阿勇",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "你？铁虎是为大老板死的？还是为了你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不管铁虎是为谁死的，我只知道大老板若是现在要我去死，我还是会立刻就去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "text": "人呢？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_ya_ba",
      "text": "你们不要害怕，我不是来害你们的，只不过想来问你们几句！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "说过！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "铁虎本来的名字，是不是叫雷震天？'风云雷虎'雷震天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "好像是的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "我好像听他自己在说，江湖中能击败雷震天的人并不多！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "text": "可是铁虎好像已认出他是什么人……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_ya_ba",
      "text": "我跟你吃了一辈子的苦，现在有了这机会，为什么要放过，我凭什么要为你那倒楣的朋友保守秘密，他给了我们什么好处？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_zhi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴之妻",
      "listener": "char_ya_ba",
      "text": "不让我说，我偏要说，你若不愿意享福，可以滚，滚得越远越好，我……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_ya_ba",
      "text": "好，好汉子，这世上能一下子就把自己老婆掐死的好汉还不多，我佩服你！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_ya_ba",
      "text": "杀你老婆的不是我，你找我干什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "竹叶青",
      "listener": "char_zi_ling",
      "text": "看来大老板还是比我强得多！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
